data.description: Welcome to Donna, a city on the grow! This gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2 bath, open concept house is ready for it’s new owner. A beautiful chandelier adorns the high decorative ceiling as you enter the house. A spacious living area, and functional kitchen is the perfect setting for welcoming family and friends. Easy access to expressway, new local eateries, and the newest shopping plazas! Close proximity to schools for easy drop offs, and a great backyard perfect for those upcoming fresh fall outdoor gatherings! Schedule your personal tour today!
